{{third-party|date=February 2017}} {{Infobox University | name = Bangabandhu Sheikh Mujibur Rahman Maritime University | native_name = | native_name_lang = | image_name = | image_size = | caption = | motto = | motto_lang = | mottoeng = We Strive For Maritime Excellence | type = [[Public university]] | established = {{start date|2013}} | chancellor = President [[Abdul Hamid (politician)|Abdul Hamid]] | president = | provost = | vice_chancellor = Real Admiral M. Khaled Iqbal BSP, ndc, psc | rector = | principal = | dean = | head_label = | head = | academic_staff = | administrative_staff = | students = | undergrad = | postgrad = | doctoral = | other = | address = Plot# 14/06-14/23, Pallabi Mirpur-12, Dhaka-1216 | city = | state = [[Dhaka]] | country = [[Bangladesh]] | postcode = <!--or, postalcode or zipcode--> | coor = | campus = | colours = | nickname = BSMRMU | affiliations = [[University Grants Commission (Bangladesh)|University Grants Commission]] | website = {{URL|bsmrmu.edu.bd}} | logo = | footnotes = }} '''Bangabandhu Sheikh Mujibur Rahman Maritime University''' ('''BSMRMU''') was established in 2013, the 37th public university of the country. It is the first maritime University in [[Bangladesh]], the 3rd maritime University in South Asia and the 12th maritime University in the world.<ref name="bsmrmu.edu.bd">{{cite web|url=http://www.bsmrmu.edu.bd/history.php|title=Welcome to BSMR Maritime University, Bangladesh|publisher=}}</ref> the University is still in an early stage; it has issued its first calls for admission in December, 2016 <ref>{{Cite web|url=http://bsmrmu.edu.bd/admission-notice.php|title=Admission notice|last=|first=|date=|website=|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=}}</ref>
==Campus== The University has its temporary campus at Pallabi, Mirpur-12 in [[Dhaka]]. But permanent campus will be established at 106 acre land at Hamidchar, Bakolia in Chittagong <ref name="bsmrmu.edu.bd"/>
==Academics== * ''Undergraduate Programs'' ** B.Sc (Hons) in Oceanography ** B.Sc (Hons) in Naval Architecture and Offshore Engineering ** BBA in Port Management and Logistics ** LLB in Maritime Law * ''Postgraduate Programs'' ** Master in Port & Shipping Management ** LLM Maritime Law ** MBA (Major in Maritime Business) * ''Short (Certificate) Courses'' ** Supply Chain Management ** Freight Forwarding ** Marine Insurance and Claim ** Dangerous Goods Handling and Transportation
